What is changed?
****************

   1.2 -> 1.3

   - bug fixes: scan routines, window nr

   - french catalog by Jerome Chesnot

   - dansk catalog by Thomas Petersen

   - polish catalog by Marcin Orlowski

   - spanish catalog by Damaso D. Estevez

   - new version of all MCCs

   1.2b5 -> 1.2

   - new parse engine

   - bug fixes: NetScape Hotlist

   - norvegian catalog by Kim Roar Utsi

   - new version of Bookmarks.mcc, Popxxx.mcp

   - sort


