@Node "Installation" "_eng.guide/Installation"
@Next "History"
@Prev "Requirements"
@Toc "Main"

How to install!
***************


     copy URLManager/Libs/MUI/*  MUI:Libs/MUI/
     copy URLManager/URLManager.prefs ENV:
     copy URLManager/URLManager(%|.info) <path>

   There are several translations of catalog files, you can copy them to
your language drawer, e.g.:


     copy URLManager/Catalogs/norsk/URLManager.catalog Locale:Catalogs/norsk/
     copy URLManager/Catalogs/français/URLManager.catalog Locale:Catalogs/français/
     copy URLManager/Catalogs/dansk/URLManager.catalog Locale:Catalogs/dansk/

   $MTL_ENG$


@EndNode

